---
import GlobalLayout from "../layouts/GlobalLayout.astro";
import site from "../config.json";
---

<GlobalLayout title="Legal & Disclosures" description="Compliance, WFG affiliation, and educational disclaimers for Glorious Destiny Advisory.">
  <section class="relative bg-ink text-ivory py-20 sm:py-24 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grain opacity-15 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold">Legal &amp; Disclosures</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-ivory/70 font-sans">Protecting you—and the integrity of this work.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-ivory">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 space-y-10 font-sans text-body/90 leading-relaxed">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Independent entity</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          {site.brand} is an independent entity. {site.principal} is a licensed financial professional with World
          Financial Group (WFG). References to WFG are for identification only and do not imply endorsement of this
          website’s contents by WFG beyond what is required for disclosure.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Educational use</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          This website is for educational purposes only. Nothing here is financial, legal, or tax advice. Past
          experiences or examples are not guarantees of future results. Products and strategies may not be available in
          all states or jurisdictions.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Your situation</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Results may vary. Consult a licensed professional for recommendations specific to your situation. Do not send
          confidential account numbers or documents through unsecured website forms.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink">WFG &amp; regulatory disclosure</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">
          Any financial professional affiliations, licenses, product availability, and regulatory disclosures should be
          reviewed for the visitor’s jurisdiction before recommendations are made.
        </p>
      </div>
      <ul class="text-sm font-semibold text-gold-deep space-y-2 pt-4 border-t border-ink/10">
        <li><a href="/privacy" class="hover:underline">Privacy Policy →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/terms" class="hover:underline">Terms of Use →</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</GlobalLayout>
